        <abstract>
            <p>Sexual behaviour of chaffinches.</p>
            <p>Numbers of female linnets in September.</p>
            <p>His experiments on brightly coloured larvae [as food], testing A. R. Wallace’s theory.</p>
            <p>His observations of a rookery make him wonder whether it may not be more difficult than we think for birds to pair.</p>
